Example brainrender scene

This is an example interactive scene created with brainrender. It shows the outline of the mouse brain and thalamus and the position of the VAL nucleus within the thalamus. All data are from the Allen Brain atlas.

You can use your mouse to move the scene around and zoom in/out.
